ets\ndisplay the full spectral, magnetic field and temperature range of the\ninstrument and demonstrate data analysis strategies. Effects from free charge\ncarriers in two dimensional confinement and in a volume material, as well as\nquantum mechanical effects (inter-Landau-level transitions) are observed and\ndiscussed exemplarily.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Jan 2014 16:23:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
